p><h2><span id=3D"How_To_Use_the_Secant_Line_Calculator">How To Use the Sec=
ant Line Calculator?</span></h2><p>You can use the&nbsp;<b>Secant Line Calc=
ulator</b> by specifying the values of the point on curve ( x, y ) and ente=
ring the function first concerning x and then y. After clicking the submit =
button you can have your desired results.</p><div id=3D"AdThrive_Content_2_=
